Security you can trust

![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674d719e8500f0f696f4503f/674f7530aebed43ce66da730_Security.svg)

Intryc is the most flexible and dynamic QA tool I've ever worked with. Since implementing it, we've reduced time spent on mundane tasks like ticket selection by 90%—which is even more impressive given the high complexity of our ticket ownership workflows.

The Intryc team's exceptional support and dedication to customizing the product for our needs have been invaluable. They made the impossible possible. Huge thanks to the team!

![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674d719e8500f0f696f4503f/675c482318fc9817d48f9faa_Thomas%20Kolovos.jpeg)

Thomas Kolovos

QA Team Lead at Blueground

Intryc offers an optimal combination of flexibility, real time workload distribution, intelligent automation, and ease of use which enable us to streamline our operations and increase the efficiency of our QA team, giving us a competitive edge.

Compared to other established solutions we’ve used in the past, which lacked dynamic features and had cumbersome reporting, Intryc stands out by addressing the key needs of a modern QA team.

![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674d719e8500f0f696f4503f/675c4815723cfd5476d7a87f_Jorge%20Portillo.webp)

Jorge Portillo

QA Lead, Operational Excellence at Deel

Since adopting Intryc, we've increased our audit output by 40% and enhanced continuous improvement insights by 130%, spanning Product, Support infrastructure, Enablement, and SOPs.

The team at Intryc has been an outstanding partner, providing exceptional support throughout the implementation process. We're excited about expanding our collaboration, especially in exploring their evolving AI capabilities.

![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674d719e8500f0f696f4503f/675c127214027c844a57d0e3_Albert.webp)

Albert Luque Strazecki

Associate Director, Operational Excellence, Deel

I’m honestly loving how Intryc is shaping up! I definitely see it becoming one of the top QA tools worldwide soon. We’re glad and honoured to be a part of this journey!

![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674d719e8500f0f696f4503f/682f254d7224ee1d367d6e96_Fadhil-Alamri.jpeg)

Fadhil Alamri

CX Specialist, Ziina

I’m really glad we found Intryc at the right time! Scaling without leveraging AI simply isn’t an option anymore.

In my opinion, what’s been most impactful is not just the workload reduction, but how it’s shifted the mindset. Seeing AI in action has shown the team that efficiency, insight, and quality can all go up at the same time.

![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674d719e8500f0f696f4503f/684abb627cd5d5b02c6bbb93_Rayan_Nasir.jpeg)

Rayan Nasir

Head of Customer Experience, Sadapay

Never thought reviewing my performance evaluation could feel like flipping through a surprisingly binge-worthy highlight reel—insightful and entertaining!

![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674d719e8500f0f696f4503f/6868bfe61ca52dce991b0c07_Aminah-Ausaf.jpeg)

Aminah Ausaf

Experience Associate, Sadapay

Key Features

### We make improving your customer support easy.

Traditional QA methods are time-consuming and limited, providing only partial insights that slow down feedback or consistent, data-driven improvements.

[View all features](https://www.intryc.com/#)

[**Sampling**\\
\\
Stop wasting hours on sampling. Use your custom rules, tags, and other attributes from your data sources and SOPs and set up statistically significant samples in minutes, not hours.](https://www.intryc.com/#w-tabs-3-data-w-pane-0) [**Evaluations with AI**\\
\\
Break through that 5% ticket sample ceiling. Train your own AI QA to your knowledge-base and SOP achieve up to 100% coverage across all scorecards, criteria, and tickets with Intryc's powerful AI.](https://www.intryc.com/#w-tabs-3-data-w-pane-1) [**Customisable scorecards**\\
\\
Your scorecard, your rules. No limits on the number of scorecards, criteria, or context included in each to ensure a world-class QA program.](https://www.intryc.com/#w-tabs-3-data-w-pane-2)

![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674d719e8500f0f696f4503f/6764272ed1bdadf1b9026d22_Tab%201.avif)

![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674d719e8500f0f696f4503f/6764272e0c1ea2f67fa7f475_Tab%202.avif)

![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674d719e8500f0f696f4503f/6764272e036316ccac3762c3_Tab%203.avif)

![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674d719e8500f0f696f4503f/6750661879a6bd789e07ca57_Noise%20BG.webp)

Proactive insights

## Know exactly what’s working and what needs attention

Intryc brings your ticket metadata together, triggering real-time alerts for any spikes or pressing issues that need immediate attention.

[View all features](https://www.intryc.com/product/monitoring/insights)

![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674d719e8500f0f696f4503f/674ffc4e83628fa6f93e4456_Intuitive%20Highlights.webp)

## Stay on top of everything

Get a high-level overview of your recent tickets and stay informed about everything happening at a glance.

## Receive real-time notifications

See instant alerts for any spikes or emerging issues, empowering you to respond swiftly and keep your service quality top-notch.

## Analyse data by key metrics

Segment data by country, product, or topic to get focused insights that matter the most to your business, without the hassle of digging.

## Effortless issue summaries

Read concise summaries, user quotes, and ticket samples to have a deep understanding of root causes.

Spotlight Features

## Deliver consistent quality, no matter the ticket load

Traditional QA methods are manual, time-consuming, and cover only a fraction of tickets or scorecards. This limits insights and slows down improvements in your team’s performance and customer experience.

[Performance Analytics\\
\\
AI-driven insights on key topics, product areas, agent performance, and customer service processes from your entire ticket base](https://www.intryc.com/#w-tabs-4-data-w-pane-0) [Agent Coaching\\
\\
Enable tailored coaching with evaluations based on your scorecards’ rating and feedback](https://www.intryc.com/#w-tabs-4-data-w-pane-1) [Detailed Ticket View\\
\\
Access complete ticket metadata, across side conversations, internal notes, and ticket events to enable end-to-end evaluations for complete performance reviews.](https://www.intryc.com/#w-tabs-4-data-w-pane-2)

![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674d719e8500f0f696f4503f/6759d45b6bc640f37eef0426_Tickets%20_%20Detailed%20viewss%203.avif)

![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674d719e8500f0f696f4503f/675031ba1affd684b454e96c_Agent%20Coaching.webp)

![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674d719e8500f0f696f4503f/675030d66bf206043e709bd6_Ticket%20View.webp)
